OL,5, Scammers are cold-calling people asking
OL,6, for their bank details to receive the  
OL,7, government's #150 energy rebate,       
OL,8, councils have warned.                  
OL,10,FChancellor Rishi Sunak announced the   
OL,11,Frebate for homes in council tax bands A
OL,12,Fto D in February to help people cope   
OL,13,Fwith escalating cost of living prices. 
OL,15,FThe Local Government Association (LGA) 
OL,16,Furged people to be alert to the scam   
OL,17,Fand not give out personal information. 
OL,19,FIt emphasised that councils would never
OL,20,Frequest bank details over the phone.   
